{"tid":1760623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱特首與民對話「百多場」 劉曉明撐林鄭工作無失敗","createTime":"2019-11-28T10:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T18:03:16.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcb398491894a936ed9dcd754ba7604ad99c314","tid":1760623,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/11/1574924333_ja-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F11%2F1574924333_ja-1280w.png&h=926aa697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉曉明。(英國廣播公司影片截圖，中國駐英大使館轉載)<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英大使劉曉明接受英國廣播公司(BBC)節目訪問，並在使館的網頁轉載對話，當中劉曉明與節目本持人討論香港修例風波。被問到特首林鄭月娥是否要下台，劉曉明稱林鄭月娥的工作做得很好，認為她的工作沒有失敗，若不是外部勢力在幕後操縱，「暴徒」不破壞特區政府與民眾對話，她就不會失敗，稱自反修例風波5個多月以來，林鄭及其團隊做了許多努力，「與民眾進行了一百多場對話交流」，但極端分子不給他們機會，重申林鄭月娥及其管治團隊仍然獲得中央政府的全力支持。<br />\n劉曉明又表示，不應該過度解讀區議會選舉中所謂「反對派取得壓倒性勝利」，指仍有四成選民沒投票給反對派，而且在任何國家的選舉中，在暴亂、動亂和經濟放緩等背景下，當政者總是容易失去更多選票，而這是因為是暴力犯罪分子造成的結果，為香港帶來了巨大麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%ae%9a%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e7%84%a1%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%97-%e5%8a%89%e6%9b%89%e6%98%8e%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b9%e8%88%87%e6%b0%91%e7%9c%be%e5%b0%8d%e8%a9%b1%e7%99%be%e5%a4%9a%e5%a0%b4-198245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e8%25ae%259a%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e6%2595%2597-%25e5%258a%2589%25e6%259b%2589%25e6%2598%258e%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25a5%25b9%25e8%2588%2587%25e6%25b0%2591%25e7%259c%25be%25e5%25b0%258d%25e8%25a9%25b1%25e7%2599%25be%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25a0%25b4-198245&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e464a2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%ae%9a%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e7%84%a1%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%97-%e5%8a%89%e6%9b%89%e6%98%8e%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b9%e8%88%87%e6%b0%91%e7%9c%be%e5%b0%8d%e8%a9%b1%e7%99%be%e5%a4%9a%e5%a0%b4-198245</a>"},{"pid":"179ae0ac625b401cbcd445e37c3ed2359329c2c2","tid":1760623,"uid":291203,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"失敗到連自己失敗都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feca4134548d4e8b385bdd774ed4fbf9b08c1b68","tid":1760623,"uid":214192,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"百幾場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同咩民溝通左百幾場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97455cc21b209445f9e512741352a85388f5aa9","tid":1760623,"uid":298012,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"圍左百幾場爐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecb9bdd22d553cbdc8d2ef2fff52fd43f38449b","tid":1760623,"uid":162008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"百幾場？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己同自己對話，自己開會？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"9017d8ee05c2f6199fdd8b68671866d0bdc4f60c","tid":1760623,"uid":55854,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"唔怪得近排話林奠自言自語"},{"pid":"289e591ebc950cd5cc23afdb3ab20f103041dbeb","tid":1760623,"uid":39838,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"百幾場?<br />\n1個人當一次?"},{"pid":"f01100fee0d6840538b280321c18120694ea0178","tid":1760623,"uid":140552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"思覺失調 及早求醫"},{"pid":"81032efcc5e648af70c174b8c0e21d0a8eda105a","tid":1760623,"uid":76674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"百幾場?<br />\n開一場claim百幾場錢?"},{"pid":"5248643ad3aa14a8f4