鄭及其團隊做了許多努力，「與民眾進行了一百多場對話交流」，但極端分子不給他們機會，重申林鄭月娥及其管治團隊仍然獲得中央政府的全力支持。<br />\n劉曉明又表示，不應該過度解讀區議會選舉中所謂「反對派取得壓倒性勝利」，指仍有四成選民沒投票給反對派，而且在任何國家的選舉中，在暴亂、動亂和經濟放緩等背景下，當政者總是容易失去更多選票，而這是因為是暴力犯罪分子造成的結果，為香港帶來了巨大麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%ae%9a%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e7%84%a1%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%97-%e5%8a%89%e6%9b%89%e6%98%8e%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b9%e8%88%87%e6%b0%91%e7%9c%be%e5%b0%8d%e8%a9%b1%e7%99%be%e5%a4%9a%e5%a0%b4-198245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e8%25ae%259a%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e6%2595%2597-%25e5%258a%2589%25e6%259b%2589%25e6%2598%258e%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25a5%25b9%25e8%2588%2587%25e6%25b0%2591%25e7%259c%25be%25e5%25b0%258d%25e8%25a9%25b1%25e7%2599%25be%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25a0%25b4-198245&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e464a2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%ae%9a%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e7%84%a1%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%97-%e5%8a%89%e6%9b%89%e6%98%8e%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b9%e8%88%87%e6%b0%91%e7%9c%be%e5%b0%8d%e8%a9%b1%e7%99%be%e5%a4%9a%e5%a0%b4-198245</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"其實依啲極權國家所謂大使<br />\n每次發言都係大力踐踏人類普世價值<br />\n西方社會聽完應更肯定香港大鑊"},{"pid":"e7d9daaa5acb69397ef8418eacab5e45317554f1","tid":1760623,"uid":297453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"feca4134548d4e8b385bdd774ed4fbf9b08c1b68","tid":1760623,"uid":214192,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"百幾場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同咩民溝通左百幾場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"點擊此處與特首展開激情對話<br />\n<br />\n地方的特首需要對話"},{"pid":"b06c7279f79e41ad44814eec2e7bf17cf89c6bdb","tid":1760623,"uid":76806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"